nded js-expand">呵呵。。。呵呵。。。孩子，喜欢加班么？喜欢英年早逝么？喜欢增加眼睛度数么？建筑设计专业欢迎你！！ 想转行还来得及~~<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/20605334/answer/21574905">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="2"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/mo-xiao-xi-74" data-hovercard='p$t$mo-xiao-xi-74'>李小ice</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/oceanely" data-hovercard='p$t$oceanely'>少糖</a></span></span> <span>赞同</span></div><script type="text" class="content">呵呵。。。呵呵。。。孩子，喜欢加班么？喜欢英年早逝么？喜欢增加眼睛度数么？建筑设计专业欢迎你！！<br><br><br><br><br>想转行还来得及~~</script><a class="time" href="/question/20605334/answer/21574905">2014-01-11</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>2</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="422549"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">4 条评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-thank "><i class="fi fi-thank"></i>感谢</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-share"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-collect"><i class="fi fi-fav"></i>收藏</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-report"><i class="fi fi-report"></i>举报</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="1"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic3.zhimg.com/5e24705bc_m.jpg"><meta name="own" content="true"><a href="/terms#sec-licence-1" target="_blank" class="action-item js-copyright">作者保留权利</a></li><li class="hid